imsmd:description.imsmd:langstring: Help the alien Zorpac to find out about plant life on Earth. Choose different combinations of leaves, seeds and roots to design a plant that is best adapted to surviving in a particular environment. Optimise the plant design to suit survival in specific environments: mangroves; cool rainforest; mountain slopes; arid land. Check results; get feedback on matching the plant features to suit the environment.
